  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为智慧教育平台画一个核心服务流转图。主要涉及课堂服务、学生数据库、成绩同步和内容分发这几个模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。这几个模块之间的数据流向是怎样的？是单向传递还是有循环依赖？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "课堂服务会调用另一个课堂服务实例做负载均衡，然后落到学生数据库。成绩同步服务需要双节点热备，最后数据还是要回写到学生数据库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主链路：ClassroomService到StudentDB，再到双节点的GradeSync。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但GradeSync第二个节点要指回StudentDB，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加回指。那ContentCDN在什么位置介入？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ContentCDN是双节点部署，从StudentDB读取用户画像后，第一个CDN节点要连第二个CDN节点做边缘同步，然后第二个节点再回查StudentDB做最终校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "稍等，您说的是CDN1→CDN2→StudentDB，还是CDN1→CDN2→StudentDB→CDN1？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是CDN1→CDN2→StudentDB，然后StudentDB再连到CDN1，形成三角校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了CDN部分的三条边。我检查一下整体结构：ClassroomService有两个节点串联，StudentDB作为中心枢纽，GradeSync双节点，CDN双节点加三角回流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，CDN部分我描述有误。StudentDB回查之后应该连到CDN2，不是CDN1。这样才是边缘节点最终生效。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，修正为StudentDB指向第二个CDN节点。现在CDN2有两条入边：来自CDN1和来自StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不对，让我再理清楚。实际流程是：从StudentDB出发，先到CDN1，CDN1同步到CDN2，然后CDN2要回到StudentDB确认，最后StudentDB再通知CDN2下发内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "明白了，重新调整：StudentDB→CDN1→CDN2→StudentDB→CDN2。这样CDN2确实有两条入边，但逻辑上说得通。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。现在整体看一下：开头ClassroomService有两个实例串联，然后到StudentDB，再到GradeSync双节点回环，最后CDN部分形成小循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下节点命名：ClassroomService两个节点都叫Education_ClassroomService？还是区分A、B实例？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用相同名称，通过箭头顺序体现流转。GradeSync和ContentCDN的双节点也用同样方式处理，保持命名简洁。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已完成。最终结构：10个节点，9条有向边，形成从ClassroomService出发，经过StudentDB中枢，贯穿GradeSync和ContentCDN两个双节点服务，最终回到CDN2的完整链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "StudentDB出现了三次，分别在第3、6、9个位置，作为数据持久化的锚点。这个节奏是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
